Sometimes it would be useful to scale bitmap fonts.
Only a few changes are needed:

BitmapFont.java:
...
    float scale=1;
...
    public void setScale (float newscale) {
        scale=newscale;
    }
...

and 2 times in draw( SpriteBatch spriteBatch, CharSequence str, float x, float y, int start, int end):

spriteBatch.draw(texture, x + lastGlyph.xoffset, y + lastGlyph.yoffset, lastGlyph.width_scale, lastGlyph.height_scale, lastGlyph.u, lastGlyph.v, lastGlyph.u2, lastGlyph.v2);
x += lastGlyph.xadvance*scale;

